-- CHUNGHWA TELECOM April Sales Fall 2.15% (Table) : 2412 TT
-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 2012-05-10T06:06:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-10/chunghwa-telecom-april-sales-fall-2-15-table-2412-tt.html
CHUNGHWA TELECOM said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 2.15% to NT$15,672,739,000 from NT$16,017,661,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales           15,672,739       16,017,661  
YOY%              -2.15%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           63,416,996       63,601,821  
YOY%              -0.29% 
=================================================================
 